<plot>Captain George Brummell is an upper-class dandy. He has to leave the army after having insulted the crown prince. This only gives him time to start a smear campaign against the prince. The prince, who is tired of all the yes-men around him, hires him as his chief advisor.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?062301</url></doc>
